This paper deals with image inpainting, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method utilizes semantic segmentation maps to guide the inpainting process, which involves machine learning techniques such as deep neural networks (cs.AI) and iterative refinement (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the evaluation of the inpainting results, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM).
